    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly showroom-grade vehicle. This specimen is in impeccable condition, reflecting a level of care and preservation seldom seen on the market. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, while the interior remains in pristine, original state, free from any signs of wear. Mechanically superior and cosmetically flawless, this car has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast. We invite you to experience this benchmark of automotive quality firsthand.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
